data.title: Iran 06 (1968)
data.meta_description: Iran 06 (1968) - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document is the 1968 volume of the Journal of the British Institute of Persian Studies. It contains the governing council members and officers of the Institute. It also outlines the aims and activities of the Institute, which include providing accommodation for scholars, conducting archaeological excavations, adding to their library collection, and publishing the annual Iran journal. The director's report summarizes guests at the Institute between June 1966 and October 1967, including archaeologists, scholars, and students from various universities conducting research in Iran.
